# Cursor harness accuracy

Read **`internal-devops/ecosystem/cursor-harness-truth.md`** first.

**Agents Window (`Cursor Agents`) ≠ Editor Window (`Cursor`).** Sync / Delete Index / Compute index exist **only in Editor Window**. From Agents: **`Cmd+Shift+P` → Open Editor Window** first.

Never tell Agents users to use palette **Index Main Repository** or **Sync** in Glass settings.
